WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.974
Look at what is behind you before you hit record.

00:00:03.024 --> 00:00:05.998
Clutter, oily rags, another customer's vehicle — all of it is on camera.

00:00:06.048 --> 00:00:09.022
A clean, organized work area says quietly, This is how I treat your

00:00:09.072 --> 00:00:12.046
car.
